sentences: Djavan Santos (born October 30, 1990), better known by his stage name D33J, is an American record producer based in Los Angeles, California.
Djavan Santos was born and raised in Los Angeles, California.
In October 2012, it was announced that he got signed to the Anticon label.
His first EP, Tide Songs, was re-released on the label in early 2013.
He released the second EP, Gravel, later that year.
